---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../styles/privacy.css";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy | causal-order"
  description="Privacy note for the causal-order documentation site."
>
  <section class="privacy-shell">
    <article class="privacy-article">
      <p class="card-kicker">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Privacy</h1>
      <p>
        This is a static documentation site for <code>causal-order</code>. It does not provide
        accounts, forms, or application-side personal data collection by&nbsp;default.
      </p>
      <p>
        The site may store a theme preference locally in your browser so dark mode or light mode
        can be remembered between visits.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is served through Cloudflare. As part of delivering and protecting the site,
        Cloudflare may process standard technical request data such as IP address, browser or
        device metadata, requested URLs, and similar network-level information.
      </p>
      <p>
        Cloudflare&apos;s handling of that infrastructure-level data is governed by Cloudflare&apos;s own
        privacy and data-handling policies.
      </p>
      <p>
        Links to external sites such as GitHub, npm, and <code>gazali.one</code> are also governed
        by those sites&apos; own privacy and data-handling policies.
      </p>
      <p>
        If analytics, forms, or other data-collecting features are added later, this page should
        be updated to reflect that change.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/guides/">Guides</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
